\c 24
\s Ukulondolozwa kwezibane
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Laya abantwana bakoIsrayeli ukuthi balethe kuwe amafutha emihlwathi acengekileyo agigelwe ukukhanyisa ukuze izibane zivuthe njalonjalo\x + Eks. 27.20,21.\x*.
\v 3 Ngaphandle kweveyili lobufakazi, ethenteni lenhlangano, uAroni uzazilungisa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* njalonjalo, kusukela kusihlwa kuze kube sekuseni; kuzakuba yisimiso esilaphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu.
\v 4 Uzalungisa izibane eluthini lwesibane olucwengekileyo phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* njalonjalo\x + Eks. 31.8; 39.37.\x*.
\s Izinkwa zokubukiswa
\p
\v 5 Uzathatha-ke impuphu ecolekileyo, ubhake ngayo amaqebelengwana alitshumi lambili; ingxenye ezimbili etshumini kuzakuba liqebelengwana elilodwa\x + Eks. 25.30.\x*.
\v 6 Uwabeke emizileni emibili, ayisithupha emzileni\x + Eks. 39.37.\x*, phezu kwetafula elicwengekileyo phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1 Kho. 7.48. 2 Lan. 4.19. 13.11. Heb. 9.2.\x*;
\v 7 futhi ubeke ku\add lowo lalowo\add* umzila inhlaka ecengekileyo, ibe yisinkwa sesikhumbuzo, umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.
\v 8 Ngalo lonke usuku lwesabatha uzakulungisa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* njalonjalo, kuvela ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli, \add y\add*isivumelwano esilaphakade\x + 1 Lan. 9.32. Nani 4.7. 2 Lan. 2.4.\x*.
\v 9 Njalo kuzakuba ngokukaAroni lokwamadodana akhe\x + 1 Sam. 21.6. Mat. 12.4. Mark. 2.26. Luka 6.4.\x*, besebekudlela endaweni engcwele\x + Eks. 29.33; 8.31; 21.22.\x*; ngoba kuyingcwelengcwele kuye, okuvela eminikelweni yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyenziwe ngomlilo, isimiso esilaphakade.
\s Imithetho emayelana lokuhlambaza lokubulala
\p
\v 10 Kwasekuphuma indodana yowesifazana umIsrayelikazi, owayeyindodana yendoda engumGibhithe, phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli. Lalindodana yomIsrayelikazi lendoda engumIsrayeli balwa enkambeni.
\v 11 Indodana yowesifazana umIsrayelikazi yasihlambaza iBizo\x + 24.16.\x*, yathuka\x + 24.14,15,23; Eks. 21.17.\x*. Basebemletha kuMozisi\x + Eks. 18.22,26.\x*. Lebizo likanina lalinguShelomithi, indodakazi kaDibiri, owesizwe sakoDani.
\v 12 Basebemfaka esitokosini\x + Nani 15.34.\x*, ukuze bachasiselwe ngokomlomo weN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Eks. 18.15,16. Nani 27.5.\x*.
\v 13 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi yathi:
\v 14 Khiphela ngaphandle kwenkamba umthuki; labo bonke abamuzwayo kababeke izandla zabo ekhanda lakhe, lenhlangano yonke imkhande ngamatshe\x + Dute. 13.9; 17.7.\x*.
\v 15 Khuluma-ke ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi: Ngulowo lalowo othuka uNkulunkulu wakhe uzathwala isono sakhe\x + 20.20; 22.9; Nani 9.13.\x*.
\v 16 Lohlambaza ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* uzabulawa lokubulawa; inhlangano yonke izamkhanda lokumkhanda ngamatshe\x + 24.11; 1 Kho. 21.10,13. Mat. 26.65,66. Mark. 14.63,64. Joha. 10.33.\x*. Njengowokuzalwa elizweni uzakuba njalo owemzini, nxa ehlambaza iBizo uzabulawa.
\p
\v 17 Lomuntu nxa etshaya loba yiwuphi umphefumulo womuntu uzabulawa lokubulawa\x + Eks. 21.12. Nani 35.31. Dute. 19.11,12,21.\x*.
\v 18 Lotshaya abulale inyamazana uzayihlawula, impilo ngempilo\x + 24.21.\x*.
\v 19 Umuntu nxa esipha-ke umakhelwane wakhe isici, njengokwenza kwakhe kuzakwenziwa njalo kuye\x + Eks. 21.24. Dute. 19.21. Mat. 5.38. 7.2.\x*,
\v 20 ukwephuka ngokwephuka, ilihlo ngelihlo, izinyo ngezinyo; njengalokho ephe umuntu isici, kuzakwenziwa njalo kuye.
\v 21 Lotshaya inyamazana ife uzayihlawula\x + 24.18. Eks. 21.33,34.\x*; lotshaya umuntu afe uzabulawa\x + 24.17.\x*.
\v 22 Lizakuba lokwahlulela okukodwa, njengowezizwe uzakuba njalo owokuzalwa elizweni\x + Nani 15.16. Eks. 12.49.19.34.\x*. Ngoba ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu.
\p
\v 23 UMozisi wakhuluma-ke ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli, ukuthi bamkhuphele ngaphandle kwenkamba umthuki, bamkhande ngamatshe\x + 24.14.\x*. Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesenza njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi.